    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once browned, transfer the sausage[s] to a clean chopping board (reserve the pan!)</p><p>Cut narrow slices widthways (about the width of a pound coin) into the <strong>hot dog sausage[s]</strong>, making sure not to cut all the way down to the base</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced hot dog sausage[s] </strong>to a <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 15-18 min or until the sausage[s] is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
