    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel and finely slice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Deseed your <strong>peppers</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p>",
