      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>parsley </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Once the sausage[s] is cooked through, add them to the pan with the stew with any <strong>remaining juices </strong>from the tray, discard the <strong>bay leaf[ves]</strong> – this is your <strong>Hungarian-style smoky sausage leczo stew</strong></p>",
